设计出来的时候，乔布斯直言有舔屏的冲动。</p>\n<p>本人在使用一些比较青睐的电子设备时，也会有类似的冲动和心理。比如我曾经有一台 dell 的 4K 的显示器，很细腻，机身又很薄，感觉很酷，反正我很喜欢。就算没有在处理什么事情，只是看着屏幕也能体验到现代科技带来的美感。甚至什么事情也不做就只是那样欣赏它。</p>\n<p>类似的心理和行为也发生在移动设备上，有时候很喜欢这个设备的设计以及手机系统，会来回的滑动屏幕来体验这种美妙的感觉。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1672065657, "replies": 43, "id": 904840}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_large.png?m=1660301119", "name": "create", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_normal.png?m=1660301119", "title": "分享创造", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/create", "topics": 19058, "footer": "", "header": "欢迎你在这里发布自己的最新作品！", "title_alternative": "Create", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_mini.png?m=1660301119", "stars": 4670, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 17, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 238695, "username": "gowl", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/gowl", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5ac2/2987/238695_mini.png?m=1672075891", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5ac2/2987/238695_normal.png?m=1672075891", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5ac2/2987/238695_large.png?m=1672075891", "created": 1499161798, "last_modified": 1672075891}, "last_reply_by": "pierswu", "last_touched": 1672123878, "title": "请大家评价一下我设计的 UI", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/904855", "created": 1672076253, "deleted": 0, "content": "![UI]( https://www.fadingurl.org/item/2252.3961.5235.5850)", "content_rendered": "<p><img alt=\"UI\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://www.fadingurl.org/item/2252.3961.5235.5850\"/></p>\n", "last_modified": 1672076253, "replies": 43, "id": 904855}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_large.png?m=1651385965", "name": "android", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_normal.pn